{
  "abstract" : [
    {
      "text" : "Get started migrating your project to the Swift 6 language mode.",
      "type" : "text"
    }
  ],
  "hierarchy" : {
    "paths" : [
      [
        "doc:\/\/org.swift.migration.6\/documentation\/MigrationGuide"
      ]
    ]
  },
  "identifier" : {
    "interfaceLanguage" : "swift",
    "url" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.migration.6\/documentation\/Swift-6-Concurrency-Migration-Guide\/MigrationStrategy"
  },
  "kind" : "article",
  "metadata" : {
    "role" : "article",
    "title" : "Migration Strategy"
  },
  "primaryContentSections" : [
    {
      "content" : [
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Enabling complete concurrency checking in a module can yield many data-race",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "safety issues reported by the compiler.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Hundreds, possibly even thousands of warnings are not uncommon.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "When faced with a such a large number of problems,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "especially if you are just beginning to learn about Swift’s data isolation",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "model, this can feel insurmountable.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "Don’t panic.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "strong"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Frequently, you’ll find yourself making substantial progress with just a few",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "changes.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "And as you do, your mental model of how the Swift concurrency system works",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "will develop just as rapidly.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "This guidance should not be interpreted as a recommendation.",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "You should feel confident about using other approaches.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name" : "Important",
          "style" : "important",
          "type" : "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Strategy",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Strategy",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "This document outlines a general strategy that could be a good starting point.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "There is no one single approach that will work for all projects.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The approach has three key steps:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Select a module",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Enable stricter checking with Swift 5",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Address warnings",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "This process will be inherently ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "iterative",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Even a single change in one module can have a large impact on the state of the",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "project as a whole.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Begin-from-the-Outside",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Begin from the Outside",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "It can be easier to start with the outer-most root module in a project.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "This, by definition, is not a dependency of any other module.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Changes here can only have local effects, making it possible to",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "keep work contained.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Your changes do not ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "need",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text" : " to be contained to the module, however.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Dependencies under your control that have ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.migration.6\/documentation\/Swift-6-Concurrency-Migration-Guide\/CommonProblems#Unsafe-Global-and-Static-Variables",
              "isActive" : true,
              "overridingTitle" : "unsafe global state",
              "overridingTitleInlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "unsafe global state",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " or",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.migration.6\/documentation\/Swift-6-Concurrency-Migration-Guide\/CommonProblems#Implicitly-Sendable-Types",
              "isActive" : true,
              "overridingTitle" : "trivially-Sendable types",
              "overridingTitleInlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "trivially-",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "code" : "Sendable",
                  "type" : "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " types",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " can be the root cause of many warnings",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "across your project.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "These can often be the best things to focus on first.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Use-the-Swift-5-Language-Mode",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Use the Swift 5 Language Mode",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "You could find it quite challenging to move a project from Swift 5 with no",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "checking directly to the Swift 6 language mode.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "It is possible, instead, to incrementally enable more of the Swift 6 checking",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "mechanisms while remaining in Swift 5 mode.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "This will surface issues only as warnings,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "keeping your build and tests functional as you progress.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "To start, enable a single upcoming concurrency feature.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "This allows you to focus on one ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "specific type",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text" : " of problem at a time.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "alignments" : [
            "left",
            "unset",
            "unset"
          ],
          "header" : "row",
          "rows" : [
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Proposal",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Description",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Feature Flag",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/swiftlang\/swift-evolution\/blob\/main\/proposals\/0401-remove-property-wrapper-isolation.md",
                      "isActive" : true,
                      "type" : "reference"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Remove Actor Isolation Inference caused by Property Wrappers",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "code" : "DisableOutwardActorInference",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/swiftlang\/swift-evolution\/blob\/main\/proposals\/0412-strict-concurrency-for-global-variables.md",
                      "isActive" : true,
                      "type" : "reference"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Strict concurrency for global variables",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "code" : "GlobalConcurrency",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/swiftlang\/swift-evolution\/blob\/main\/proposals\/0418-inferring-sendable-for-methods.md",
                      "isActive" : true,
                      "type" : "reference"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Inferring ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code" : "Sendable",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " for methods and key path literals",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "code" : "InferSendableFromCaptures",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "type" : "table"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "These can be enabled independently and in any order.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "After you have addressed issues uncovered by upcoming feature flags,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "the next step is to ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.migration.6\/documentation\/Swift-6-Concurrency-Migration-Guide\/EnableDataRaceSafety",
              "isActive" : true,
              "overridingTitle" : "enable complete checking",
              "overridingTitleInlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "enable complete checking",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " for the module.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "This will turn on all of the compiler’s remaining data isolation checks.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Address-Warnings",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Address Warnings",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "There is one guiding principle you should use as you investigate",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "warnings: ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "express what is true now",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "strong"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Resist the urge to refactor your code to address issues.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "You will find it beneficial to minimize the amount of change necessary to",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "get to a warning-free state with complete concurrency checking.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "After that is done, use any unsafe opt-outs you applied as an indication of",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "follow-on refactoring opportunities to introduce a safer isolation mechanism.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "To learn more about addressing common problems, see ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.migration.6\/documentation\/Swift-6-Concurrency-Migration-Guide\/CommonProblems",
                  "isActive" : true,
                  "type" : "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text" : ".",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name" : "Note",
          "style" : "note",
          "type" : "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Iteration",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Iteration",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "At first, you’ll likely be employing techniques to disable or workaround",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "data isolation problems.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Once you feel like you’ve reached the stopping point for a higher-level module,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "target one of its dependencies that has required a workaround.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "You don’t have to eliminate all warnings to move on.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Remember that sometimes very minor changes can have a significant impact.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "You can always return to a module once one of its dependencies has been",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "updated.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind" : "content"
    }
  ],
